lines: 1. Gochi' as'ens'engiya ng'umbu,Malaika bagotera,Haleluy'as' Omotoria.Hosan' as'Omogambi;Togotara noboremu,Tokoragwa na Tata,Korw'ense y'ebibenobororo goch'ens' engiya.
Omogoko togoika,Natobeke chigutwa;As'ens'eria engiya,As'ens'eyi' engiya ng'umbu.
2. 'Bachenu bande mbachit-'asen'eyio riria kare.'Ngaki bono yaerire,Erio naintwe tosoe;Ntogende bosio rioka,Tobe nabwo batorigwe,Ntotogi' Erieta riaye botamb'as'ens'eyi' engiya
3. As'ens'eyio obomenyobwarosigw'ase bonsi,'Ba begenet' Omotoriana koigw'eriogi riaye;'Ngaki y'omogoko ngoch'er-'Omonen' arachike,Toyetig'ense ey'embe,Togend' as'ense'eri engiya.
